{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-02734/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-02734"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:27:34"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["extreme close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman looks around her in nervousness."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-02734","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-02734"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1/bb6b97a6-f04b-4774-9a13-d3429d60fccd","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:32:56.733Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma’s face registers discomfort as she is placed on a pedestal and judged by the Woodcock siblings. Amy Greenhough calls Reynolds a “monstrous, vampiric [threat] that become[s a] symbol of the desire that fuels capitalism and the ways in which that desire is inextricable from the bodies that contain it” (Greenhough, “Spinning Bodies into Gold,” 198).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:494.52589105581706,193.31540013449904,590.0739744451917,578.4532616005379"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1/c2ff367f-a6ba-4547-aec0-dab65f35d223","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:33:22.000Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Though Alma previously promised Reynolds that she would win any staring contest they had, she turns away from Cyril’s gaze. While she may feel confident with or equal to Reynolds, Cyril’s presence has disquieted her and left her feeling uneasy. As she grows surer of herself, Alma grows much more able to hold her own with Cyril and not shy away from her gaze.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02734/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1155.6153328850035,177.82111634162746,521.6408876933422,351.2037659717553"}}}]}]}]}